pe":"entry","text":"venue decoration 会场布置","headword":"venue decoration"},{"type":"entry","text":"invitation [ˌɪnvɪˈteɪʃn]","headword":"invitation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.邀请；请帖"},{"type":"note","text":"◎invitation letter邀请函"},{"type":"entry","text":"theme [θiːm]","headword":"theme"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.主题"},{"type":"entry","text":"media [ˈmiːdiə]","headword":"media"}]},{"number":1345,"blocks":[{"type":"definition","text":"n.媒体"},{"type":"note","text":"◎media coverage媒体报道"},{"type":"entry","text":"press section 新闻处","headword":"press section"},{"type":"entry","text":"industry departments 行业部门","headword":"industry departments"},{"type":"entry","text":"social organization 社会组织","headword":"social organization"},{"type":"entry","text":"supporter [səˈpɔːtə(r)]","headword":"supporter"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.协作单位"},{"type":"entry","text":"exclusive interview 独家采访","headword":"exclusive interview"},{"type":"entry","text":"source [sɔːs]","headword":"source"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.信息来源；原始资料"},{"type":"entry","text":"news release 新闻稿","headword":"news release"},{"type":"entry","text":"release news 发布新闻","headword":"release news"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"text","text":"有趣的小词over"}]},{"number":1346,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"知道老外怎么向自己喜欢的人表白吗？知道他们又是怎样表达“分"},{"type":"text","text":"手”吗？在表达这两个意思时老外都用到了over一词哦！"},{"type":"text","text":"1. I'm all over you. 我对你非常着迷。"},{"type":"text","text":"All over sb.的意思就是“对…非常着迷”，与之意思相近的一个习"},{"type":"text","text":"语是have a crush on sb.，所以这句话还可以说成I have a crush on you。"},{"type":"text","text":"如果下次碰上令自己非常着迷的人，你就可以用这两句话来表白哦！"},{"type":"text","text":"2. I'm over you. 我跟你之间完了。"}]}]}